    "2022), and Cardboard HMDs (10%) were used in those experiences related to reducing PTSD by watching 360° videos (e.g., Park et al. 2017).",
    "Finally, in Ergonomics and Tourism and Marketing, Cardboard and Standalone devices were not used, because user reactions to what the users were looking at could not be seen with those devices.",
    "Therefore, Desktop 6DOF HMDs were preferred in almost every paper (e.g., Luangrath et al. 2022; Erkan 2021).",
    "iVR application development differed in each case.",
    "14.8% of the studies under analysis referred to the purchase of the application for two reasons: the expense of application development, and the research group knowledge of iVR application development."
